hopobject.body: Could you give me some smaller notes? docetaxel or paclitaxel And it has a personality, says Simmons. "There are no predators but there is an obsession with the germ of evil in this paradisical land. We are uncomfortable with the image of perfection and paradise, and so we are always looking for what might be wrong. The dark, gothic version of a menacing landscape is definitely one of its 'moods' and Top of the Lake has some of that."
